NAME
    Acme::BadFont - Cope with a bad font in your editor

SYNOPSIS
      use warnings;
      use Acme::BadFont;

      my $f = "1OO";
      print $f + 1, "\n";   # 101
      my $d = "I.S";
      print $d * 2, "\n";   # 3

DESCRIPTION
    If the font in your editor is bad, this module will help by fixing the
    numbers in your strings.

